description: Team Fighters links up with Grand Chief Lupe as they track down the Death Egg. As they deal with the ferocious Felidae Warriors and Dark Egg Legion, a mysterious figure tracks them. Meanwhile, in “Heart to Heart,” Nicole and Mina finally confront each other!
name: Loyalty, Part One

description: An epic fantasy set in an ancient Greek "techno-Byzantine," Mediterranea is menaced by a mysterious swarm. Winged creatures from the east threaten the peace of this kingdom, slaughtering anything that comes between them and their goal. Alonisso's nightmares seem to be connected to these mysterious enemies, but not even the wise Auraki seems to know how.

While Planters and Fulton fight for their lives under enemy fire, Ananti confides in Ian, unaware that he has a secret of his own. Meanwhile, Warner struggles with the knowledge that their mission will ultimately force them to abandon the children of Neverland, and Doctor Federman grows more suspicious.

Demons invade the Carnival at Venice. These horrible nightmare-reflections of beloved fairytale characters are determined to tear a hole from their twisted world to ours. Demon Hunter Gabriel must force the demoness Cinderella, monster Little Mermaid, and countless others back through the portal before the last night of Carnival - else no one will live happily ever after!

Issue 3 begins right where issue two left off as Mowglii is dealing with a harsh truth and remembering how things once here. She later finds herself in the clutches of the enemy. But, through chaos, may just find an opportunity to escape. All eyes are on Mowglii as she struggles through the trials she is faced with.raven gregory

volume.name: Grimm Fairy Tales presents The Jungle Book

description:
The end of the beginning is here as Alice finally confronts the ruler of Wonderland and faces off against her greatest fear.

With the fate of both Wonderland and earth at stake, will Alice find a way to defeat madness in its purest form or will she fall to victim to the Jabberwocky's sinister machinations. The final chapter is here in this oversized issue. Includes over an unbelievable tri-fold Last Supper Tea Party cover by Zenescope artist Anthony Spay!

volume.name: Grimm Fairy Tales presents Alice In Wonderland

name: The Night That Changed My Life

description:
In this title collecting the first six issues of the DC Comics – The New 52 event, Oliver Queen is armed with cutting-edge weaponry and illegally gained intel (courtesy of his team at QCore)! As Green Arrow, he's shooting first and asking questions later as he travels the world to bring outlaws to justice...and breaking every law there is in the process.

Back Blurb

THE WORLD'S GREATEST ARCHER HAS A TARGET ON HIS BACK!

The masked vigilante Green Arrow is used to looking for trouble, but now trouble's come looking for him!

Enter Rush and his gang of thrill-seeking trust fund babies, buying their super powers and treating the world as their playground. Addicted to the celebrity their destructive behavior brings, their next stunt promises global fame: killing a super hero live on the internet --- and Green Arrow is in the crosshairs!

Now the odds are stacked against Oliver Queen, the man behind the Green Arrow mask. Even with cutting-edge weapons and tech from his Q-Core support team, Seattle's Emerald Archer will be tested as never before. Rush and his gang, the rotting man-monster Midas, the impossible assassin Blood Rose and her inhuman secret: place your bets --- but never get against Green Arrow!

GREEN ARROW: THE MIDAS TOUCH collects issues #1-6 if the New 52 series by Dan Jurgens (SUPERMAN), J.T. KRUL (CAPTAIN ATOM), KEITH GIFFEN (O.M.A.C.) and GEORGE PÉREZ (WORLD'S FINEST).
name: Volume 1

description: Jacob, armed with the Sword of Justice continues his quest to discover the source of the rage plague near Staalbreak! If left unchecked, this evil may threaten all of Sanctuary!
name: Sword of Justice

  • Pussy Cat

  • Long Ago...

  • The Cat Lady

The second art book by Kevin J. Taylor, creator, writer and artist of such books as "Model By Day", "Fang", "Girl" and currently "Girl, The Second Coming". This art book premieres unpublished works done mainly for himself, and a few commissioned works. Inside are paintings inspired by celebrities, supermodels and... panties. You'll be amazed at how much sharper his paintings have become!

Pin-up art has been appreciated for decades - a guilty pleasure that's kept generations of pop art aficionados smiling quietly to themselves! To honor the best and newest in the field, FLIRT! takes an up-close and personal look at the artists who make bad girls look soooo good! In this premiere volume, the illustrations of Carlos Cartagena and Sean Gallimore are showcased.
name: Volume 1

description: Sometimes a photo just can’t capture the ephemeral quality of a guy’s fantasy female. The painting leaves just enough for the imagination to fill in those most important blanks!To this end, we proudly present the second volume of Flirt! The Art of Naughty! See paintings from around the world celebrating the female form in all its majestic curves, hills, and valleys! Cover painting by Michal Dutkeiwicz.
name: Volume 2

description:
There's really no such thing as bad girls.

Or wicked vixens.

Or nasty brats.

Just naughty girls!

Young ladies who simply need the firm hand of an older gent to put them back on the road to proper etiquette.

That's Joe Pekar's story, and he's sticking to it like a lollipop to a car seat!

If you enjoy pillow-fights, panty-pulls, and pretty girls all in a row, Mister Pekar has just the collection of work for you!
name: Naughty Girls!

description:
"Cheeky", "saucy", "randy" are some British euphemisms that can be employed when describing the works of Archie Dickens. An Englishman from the old school, his fondness for lovely young innocents in not-so-innocent situations has delighted pin-up enthusiasts for several generations. Angelic faces with devilish designs has always been the hallmark of this illustrator. Each work reflects his sly wit and brilliant talent.

Back Blurb

"Cheeky", "saucy", "randy" and a variety of other British Euphemisms can be employed when describing the works of Archie Dickens. An Englishman from the old school, his fondness for lovely young innocents in not-so-innocent situations has delighted pin-up enthusiasts throughout the world for several generations. A contemporary of such cheesecake gods as Gil Elvgren and Alberto Vargas, Archie Dickens has been able to do what they could not - successfully span TWO centuries.

STILL painting his unique brand of pretty girls well into his nineties, it seems Archie's been able to find the secret to longevity is the sight of a pretty girl.

Then there's hope for us all!

volume.name: The Pin-Up Art of Archie Dickens

description: The spry and devilishly creative pin-up elder-statesman Archie Dickens is back with a new compendium of cuties to delight an appreciative public. A contemporary of such artistic greats as Elvgren and Vargas, Mr. Dickens was still kicking and making naughty portraits of young ladies in various states of undress into the 21st Century - all with a sly smile and an innocent demeanor. Vintage eye candy!

volume.name: The Pin-Up Art of Archie Dickens

description:
Artist, writer, musician, film-maker,Star Wars mega-fan/illustrator - Matt Busch goes by many titles. Known as "The Rock Star of Illustration", Matt puts his heart and soul into every painting. In this first-ever collection of his work, you can see the drive and the passion of his craft! The force is INDEED strong with this one!

Back Blurb

You've seen his art grace the posters, books, and comics of such notable properties as STAR WARS, LORD OF THE RINGS, and WITCHBLADE. Now, the critically acclaimed "Rock Star of Illustration" shows off a new side to his art. Here, Matt Busch shares over 100 pieces from a collection of his most glamourous, sexiest pin-up paintings ever!

Introduction by John Dolmayan of the band SYSTEM OF A DOWN!

volume.name: Pucker: The Seductive Art of Matt Busch

description:
Dr. Case's life had been quite predictable until Andrea showed up at her office. "I'm addicted to sex and I can make others addicted too!" she said. Case's only chance of discovering Andrea's hidden passions lay in Andrea's past lives. One by one Andrea pulls back the layers of unbridled passion and sensuous acts to reveal its origin. Can Case resist its ultimate temptation?

Chapter Titles

  • Foreword
  • Prologue: The City - Today
  • Chapter One: Egyptian Sojourn
  • Chapter Two: A Servant's Life
  • Chapter Three: Capturing Florence
  • Chapter Four: Paris: City of Passion
  • Chapter Five: The Voyeur
  • Chapter Six: Three Way Club
  • Chapter Seven: Seduction
  • Chapter Eight: Office Politics (Mislabeled as Chapter Seven)

name: In Love With A Wonderful Guy
